# SyncForm conventions

## Layout

- Top bar: watermark DateTimePicker, Start Sync, mock checkbox, status.
- Tabs: Sync Log, Toggl Clients (CheckedListBox), Mapping, Settings.
- Prefer editing `SyncForm.Designer.cs` for control layout; keep async/event wiring in `SyncForm.cs`.

## Mapping grid

- One grid: Toggl client + Toggl project → Spesnet project → Spesnet client → Spesnet work task.
- Reload Spesnet clients when the Spesnet project combo changes (`GetClientsByProject` / reference cache).
- Persist selections/mappings on close and before sync via `SaveMappingsFromUi`.

## Behaviour

- Disable sync/refresh buttons while async work runs.
- Marshal logger UI updates with `Invoke`/`BeginInvoke` when needed.
- On load: restore watermark, settings, mappings; optionally auto-load Spesnet reference (especially mock).
- Require Spesnet reference cache + ≥1 checked Toggl client before starting sync.
